01:42.000 --> 01:48.000
Your frame of reference is correct for you, but not for the rest of the universe.

01:48.000 --> 01:54.000
Around five kilometers from you, where the horizon begins, the ground noticeably curves away from you.

01:54.000 --> 01:59.000
